.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, disco, dubstep, d&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of funk is somewhere between the person who's sport is golf and the fan of d&b##7
3. the fan of dubstep is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the fan of disco is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco | funk | d&b       | dubstep |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, reading, rock-climbing, video-games
House: farmhouse, cottage, victorian, wooden
1. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
2. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the wooden house is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
5. the wooden house is on the left of the victorian house##1
6. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing   | video-games | reading |
| House   | farmhouse      | cottage | wooden      | victorian |

