.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, mirinda, sprite
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, december, february, august
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
6. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in december##7
7. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | 7up      | mirinda | sprite     |
| Birthday   | july    | august | december   | february |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapefruit, orange, pepper
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, pink, ebony, emerald
1. the person who likes white is on the far left##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes emerald is somewhere between the person eating cherry and the person eating orange##7
5. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
6. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | pepper    | cherry   | grapefruit | orange  |
| Color   | white | ebony | emerald    | pink |

