.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, siglo, oliveros, bolivar
4 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rabbit
1. the siglo-smoker is not the owner of the rabbit##6
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
3. the bolivar-smoker is the owner of the horse##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere between the bolivar-smoker and the havana-smoker##7
5. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar   | bolivar | oliveros | siglo | havana |
| Pet           | horse   | rabbit    | dog       | hamster  |

