.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
City: paris, new-york, nizza, edinburgh
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, pop, r&b, techno
1. the person traveling to paris is not the fan of classical##6
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the fan of techno##1
5. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person traveling to new-york##7
6. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| City           | edinburgh | paris | nizza | new-york |
| Music-Genre   | techno         | r&b      | classical | pop            |

