.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, satire, thriller, western
There 4 different types of food: peach, kiwi, raspberry, cabbage
1. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person eating cabbage##7
2. the person watching satire movies is not the person eating raspberry##6
3. the person eating kiwi is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating cabbage##5
5. the person watching family movies is the person eating peach##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Food           | peach    | kiwi   | cabbage  | raspberry      |

