2. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person eating grapefruit##6
4. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
6. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating corn##7

.:: Answer ::.
