.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish, snake
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, pop, jazz, country
1. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the fan of disco and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of pop##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
4. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | ferret    | goldfish | snake     | dog |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | country  | pop | disco |

 